1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,050 --> 00:02:19,360
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,920
Xu Yourong and I have a marriage contract.

7
00:02:22,110 --> 00:02:25,410
[Previously]

8
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,480
She is my fiancée.

9
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,320
Of course she can't marry someone else.

10
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,680
How dare you three little brats

11
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,240
speak rudely?

12
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:32,040
When dealing with shameless people,

13
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,250
[800 Li Red River]

14
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,800
you have to

15
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:35,320
slap him in the face.

16
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:36,920
Master,

17
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:39,040
I didn't mean to hide my identity.

18
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:40,970
On behalf of the Lishan Sword Sect,

19
00:02:40,970 --> 00:02:42,410
I'm asking the State Religious Academy

20
00:02:42,410 --> 00:02:43,600
to teach us something.

21
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,350
I want us

22
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,700
to top the Imperial Court Exam together.

23
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,640
Since childhood, I told you

24
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,880
the Tianhai name

25
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,210
must not be insulted by outsiders.

26
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,080
Do we have to leave?

27
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:09,840
This is the best arrangement.

28
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:21,280
[Marrow Cleansing Theory]

29
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,120
Director,

30
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,510
I just heard from that fortune-teller
who sells flower lanterns

31
00:03:26,510 --> 00:03:30,640
that people from the Li Palace came early
this morning and escorted Princess Luo away.

32
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:32,040
I'll admit I'll miss her.

33
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,040
But Luo revealed her identity
because of me.

34
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,800
The Li Palace is probably worried
about her safety

35
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,680
and took her in for protection.

36
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,960
You two—one a silly bear,

37
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,240
the other far too naïve.

38
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:42,840
If you ask me, it's most likely
the Tianhai family's dirty trick.

39
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,960
As long as Luo was here,

40
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,690
they wouldn't dare make a move.

41
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,720
But once she's away,

42
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:52,090
they can carry out their revenge
without restraint.

43
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:00,280
Move aside!

44
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,720
Silver armor with a phoenix emblem...

45
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:04,380
They're the Yongxue Army
of the Tianhai family!

46
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:11,490
They're heading straight
for the State Religious Academy!

47
00:04:11,490 --> 00:04:13,040
The streets outside are full of soldiers.

48
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:14,300
They're not friendly.

49
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,360
Just what I need to pass the time!

50
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:19,360
It'd be even better
if we could get into a little fight!

51
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,240
A warhorse?

52
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,840
You could knock down the gate,

53
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:56,200
or smash it with stones.

54
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,840
Why set the horse on fire?

55
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,400
Article 67
of the Grand Zhou Military Code:

56
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,480
Anyone who kills military horses

57
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,560
shall face severe punishment

58
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,220
and be exiled to the frontier.

59
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,760
What does the Grand Zhou Military Code
have to do

60
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:06,990
[Tianhai Shengxue,
General of the Northern Cavalry]

61
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:07,520
with our Tianhai family?

62
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,920
The young master of the Tianhai family,

63
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,640
commander of the Yongxue Army.

64
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:15,440
Rumour has it that he once killed
hundreds of demon soldiers all by himself.

65
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:18,360
He's the brightest star among the younger
generation of the Grand Zhou Army,

66
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,560
and the older brother of Tianhai Ya'er.

67
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:22,120
You're here to settle the score?

68
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:24,200
Today, I'll let you know

69
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:26,240
that without Bai Luoheng's protection,

70
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,080
you're just like this dead horse.

71
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,680
Nothing but worthless lives!

72
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,280
We'll show the world

73
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,800
that from now on,

74
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:36,060
-there will be no State Religious—
-Quit the babbling!

75
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,840
Where did this idiot come from?

76
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,800
You talk too much!

77
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,460
Silly bear,

78
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,150
aim properly next time.

79
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,880
You like burning things?

80
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,840
Setting sun hangs low!

81
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:47,500
I'll let you burn all you want!

82
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,060
Be careful.

83
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,840
This idiot is in the Realm of
Approaching the Profound Truth!

84
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:57,480
Form up,

85
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,280
kill them all!

86
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,010
Snow-Shatter Army-Breaking Formation!

87
00:06:04,010 --> 00:06:04,930
A three-sided formation,

88
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:07,430
[Snow-Shatter Army-Breaking Formation]

89
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,000
with the soldiers' True Essence
linked together

90
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,840
like an avalanche crashing down.

91
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:08,520
Xuanyuan Po,

92
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:09,680
left flank—use Earth-Shaking Rock Thrust.

93
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,280
Thirty-Six,

94
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:12,410
right flank—Evening Clouds Retract.

95
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,810
I prefer to take them all out together!

96
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,000
Not bad,

97
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,800
you've learned to take over my job!

98
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,860
Have a taste of Wenshui's specialty!

99
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,400
Evening Clouds Retract!

100
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,160
Yeshi Step.

101
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,320
Although I don't have True Essence yet,

102
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,360
the basic footwork

103
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,820
should be enough
to deal with these cavalry.

104
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:46,080
You broke the Yongxue Armys formation.

105
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:48,040
No wonder Ya'er fell to you.

106
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,360
Good.

107
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,200
That

108
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,020
makes this more interesting.

109
00:06:53,650 --> 00:06:56,100
[Destiny Star, Furious Snowstorm]

110
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,440
Darn it,

111
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,120
what kind of formation is this?

112
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,810
Is it supposed to cool us down?

113
00:07:06,890 --> 00:07:10,350
I'll show you bumpkins

114
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,600
what a real battlefield

115
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,960
looks like!

116
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,000
Shoot!

117
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,360
His True Essence is strong.

118
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,159
We can't fight him head-on.

119
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,720
So this is the formation he used

120
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,520
to kill all those demon soldiers?

121
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:40,200
I don't mind adding you three to the mix!

122
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,159
Time to see

123
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:44,659
what an Eight-Foot Snowstorm
can really do!

124
00:07:47,409 --> 00:07:48,850
[Ice Fang Prison]

125
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:59,620
Do folks of that Realm really have
that much True Essence?

126
00:07:59,620 --> 00:08:01,040
It's not just the ice bullets—

127
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,580
the cold is slowing us down.

128
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,360
If this drags on, we'll lose.

129
00:08:09,210 --> 00:08:11,080
[Flame-Draw Sword Art]

130
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:17,600
Are you sure you want to do this?

131
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,240
Worthless fool
without even True Essence,

132
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,760
how dare you fight me?

133
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:21,880
What a death wish!

134
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,360
Think carefully.

135
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,480
I wouldn't want to kill you by accident!

136
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,080
This is the only way
to break the formation.

137
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:28,840
Trust me!

138
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,890
Your clumsy demon footsteps

139
00:08:30,910 --> 00:08:34,080
won't keep you alive
in the Eight-Foot Snowstorm forever.

140
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,440
I'll put an end to this!

141
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,400
Now!

142
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,200
Xuanyuan!

143
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:39,760
Okay!

144
00:08:39,970 --> 00:08:41,039
Hengshan Leap!

145
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,280
This is my last bit of True Essence.

146
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,300
Take him down!

147
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:52,700
He actually wants to ignite himself
to break my Snowstorm?

148
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:55,400
One wrong move
and he'll burn himself alive.

149
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,520
What a lunatic.

150
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,440
But what's the point?

151
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,120
Die!

152
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:17,280
What?

153
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,400
This sword...

154
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,800
I can't block it?

155
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,120
Impossible!

156
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,040
You

157
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,280
lost.

158
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,480
We won!

159
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:39,520
-We won!
-Not bad.

160
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,120
What kind of sword is this?

161
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,640
It can even harness the fire

162
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:45,570
to break my Eight-Foot Snowstorm?

163
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,920
Such a pity...

164
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,520
Young Master,

165
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,880
there's no need for you

166
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,840
to handle this trash yourself.

167
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,480
Go!

168
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:07,680
Remind the whole world

169
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:09,520
that those who offend the Tianhai family

170
00:10:09,450 --> 00:10:12,440
[Fei Dian, Divine General of Grand Zhou]

171
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,400
must die.

172
00:10:15,930 --> 00:10:18,330
You old dog of the Star-Gathering Realm...

173
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:29,400
No matter how talented you are,

174
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,480
a Divine General can destroy you
with a snap of the fingers!

175
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,320
Using your age to pick on kids?

176
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,720
Hundreds of years gone

177
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:37,600
and you're still this pathetic,

178
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,360
Fei Dian!

179
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:42,920
Jin Yulyu?

180
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:45,520
Weren't you
supposed to be at the Li Palace?

181
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,680
Thanks to you,

182
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:49,720
Princess Luo is safe there

183
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,480
under the protection of the Grand Pontiff.

184
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:54,480
That's why I had the chance
to come back and take a look.

185
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:59,800
The most important thing about studying
is peace and quiet.

186
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,530
I heard you're short a doorman?

187
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:03,680
Indeed!

188
00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:05,120
You name the price!

189
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:09,420
Do you know the consequences
of going against the Tianhai family?

190
00:11:12,070 --> 00:11:14,180
That slap felt so good!

191
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,640
Impressive!

192
00:11:16,310 --> 00:11:18,040
Fei Dian is ranked Sixth Divine General,

193
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:20,770
yet he couldn't even dodge
a single slap from him.

194
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,390
Emperor Baidi also agreed

195
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:30,210
to place Princess Luoheng
under the Grand Pontiff's supervision,

196
00:11:30,210 --> 00:11:32,720
ending the protection
of the State Religious Academy.

197
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,880
As a subject,

198
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,330
do you intend to defy your Emperor's will?

199
00:11:37,450 --> 00:11:40,280
I resigned hundreds of years ago.

200
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,200
Baidi

201
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,520
has no say over me!

202
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,680
I answer only to Her Highness now!

203
00:11:55,810 --> 00:11:58,110
How dare you insult me like that!

204
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,800
Jin Yulyu,

205
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:03,470
you've gone too far!

206
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:07,000
This is the power
of the Star-Gathering Realm?

207
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,840
Star Domain!

208
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,790
50 years ago,

209
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:11,670
on the northern battlefield,

210
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:14,000
you humiliated me.

211
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:16,720
I endured hardship,
honed my skills for years.

212
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,800
Today,

213
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:20,000
I'll settle both old and new grudges

214
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:22,440
at once!

215
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:26,530
Ignore it.

216
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:28,360
It's just some young ones fooling around.

217
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:31,080
Yet those old relics insist on
stirring up trouble...

218
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:33,040
Truly unbecoming.

219
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:40,640
So this is how battles
between Divine Generals play out.

220
00:12:40,640 --> 00:12:42,440
Good thing it's not every day.

221
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:44,370
Otherwise, Shendu would be...

222
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,440
Watch closely.

223
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,140
This

224
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,500
is how you use the Star Domain!

225
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,660
Thousand-Feather Thunderclap!

226
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:14,760
The Star Domain
I've honed for fifty years!

227
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,320
You!

228
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:24,640
Could your Yao form be—

229
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:42,880
That was amazing!

230
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:44,720
You're far too talented
to just be a doorman.

231
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,580
Please stay and be our teacher.

232
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:48,000
Master Divine General,

233
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,080
I want to learn that move you just used!

234
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,040
Senior,

235
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:54,240
do you really think you can stay and guard
the State Religious Academy forever?

236
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,680
Why not?

237
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:58,480
Then let's stake the honor
of the Tianhai family.

238
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,040
Guards!

239
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,890
Send in the Imperial Guard!

240
00:14:00,920 --> 00:14:03,440
I'll fight the State Religious Academy
to the death today!

241
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:05,160
Prince Chen Liu has arrived!

242
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:19,190
Brother,

243
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:19,880
I—

244
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,640
Her Majesty is watching.

245
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:23,840
A childish quarrel that goes too far

246
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,170
is hardly appropriate.

247
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:26,460
You should return.

248
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,520
Dare to face me again

249
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:31,520
at this year's Imperial Court Exam?

250
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:32,200
Sure.

251
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,600
We'll beat you again.

252
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:34,720
You—

253
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:43,760
Director Chen!

254
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:45,560
Director Chen!

255
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:46,940
Director Chen!

256
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,440
Director Chen!

257
00:14:48,460 --> 00:14:49,400
Director Chen!

258
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,160
Are you hurt?

259
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,480
In broad daylight,

260
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,560
you break into our gate

261
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:56,960
and injure our director.

262
00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:57,840
And you think

263
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,360
you can just walk away?

264
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:01,480
It's just some trivial matter.

265
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,610
Watch your tongue, you petty one!

266
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:05,760
It's merely children playing around,

267
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:07,680
no need to make a mountain
out of a molehill.

268
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:09,070
Greetings, Prince Chen Liu.

269
00:15:09,070 --> 00:15:10,480
This has nothing to do with you.

270
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:11,560
Trivial matter?

271
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:12,770
Who are you kidding?

272
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:15,360
You stormed the Academy
with the Yongxue Army,

273
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,480
making the whole town witness it.

274
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:18,200
And now that you've lost,

275
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,120
you think you can just sneak off?

276
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,620
How unbecoming!

277
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,280
Don't go!

278
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,360
According to the Zhou law,

279
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,920
you should at least

280
00:15:25,920 --> 00:15:27,640
pay the repair and medical fees.

281
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:29,800
You're the first of the young generation
of the Tianhai family,

282
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:32,460
surely you wouldn't skip out
on the bill, right?

283
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,160
Fine!

284
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,960
It's just a broken door,

285
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:41,100
I'll fix it for you!

286
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,000
That's right,

287
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,930
you only managed to break one door.

288
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:48,040
Wait,

289
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,400
didn't you say

290
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:50,130
you were here

291
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:52,200
to destroy
the entire State Religious Academy?

292
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,320
That door was taken out by a warhorse.

293
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,920
You didn't even get a chance
to do anything else.

294
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:56,160
Just leave the door like this.

295
00:15:56,160 --> 00:15:56,960
It's fine.

296
00:15:58,520 --> 00:15:59,240
Brilliant.

297
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:05,120
Truly brilliant.

298
00:16:05,850 --> 00:16:07,740
With the door left open,

299
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:10,280
everyone in Shendu can see

300
00:16:10,410 --> 00:16:13,240
just how arrogant and overbearing
someone is.

301
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:16,640
Let's go!

302
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,760
The State Religious Academy
lives up to its reputation!

303
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:21,320
It's got real spirit!

304
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,520
Impressive!

305
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,460
You don't have to thank me.

306
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:33,080
If anything comes up from now on,

307
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:33,880
let me know.

308
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:43,040
Life

309
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:45,640
is the most precious thing in the world.

310
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:48,040
It should never be trampled like this.

311
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:50,600
Emperor Taizong established the Horse
Division and the Imperial Stud Office

312
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,400
to implement horse management.

313
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,080
How much effort did it take

314
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:56,720
for commoners
to raise a warhorse like that...

315
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:59,280
The Tianhai family
has long styled themselves as royalty.

316
00:16:59,280 --> 00:17:01,560
They don't even care
about the lives of the people,

317
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:02,880
let alone a horse.

318
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:05,810
If you don't like a world like this,

319
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:07,480
then we'll change it.

320
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,760
If you can't stand it,

321
00:17:10,319 --> 00:17:11,599
then you simply don't have to.

322
00:17:11,599 --> 00:17:12,200
Very well.

323
00:17:12,359 --> 00:17:13,280
I'll provide the funds.

324
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:14,609
I'll provide the sweat.

325
00:17:17,490 --> 00:17:18,569
Watching them

326
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,920
reminds me of

327
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:23,040
how vibrant this place used to be.

328
00:17:23,930 --> 00:17:27,089
It's another era of wildflowers in bloom.

329
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:32,640
[The Era of Wildflowers in Bloom]

330
00:17:32,670 --> 00:17:35,900
[The Wind Rises Among the Ivy, Episode 7]

331
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:47,810
The warning talisman has been triggered?

332
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:56,230
[To be continued]

333
00:17:58,290 --> 00:17:59,430
You've been watching for so long,

334
00:17:59,430 --> 00:18:01,260
why not join the State Religious Academy?

335
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:03,660
Remember to scan the code
to register here!

336
00:18:04,760 --> 00:18:08,080
We've arranged
an interesting test for you.

337
00:18:05,020 --> 00:18:08,300
[In the next episode]

338
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:09,560
Turn back.

339
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,240
Today,

340
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:12,440
you won't be entering the Li Palace.

341
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:15,290
The Qingteng Banquet
is just the appetizer,

342
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:13,780
[I miss you]

343
00:18:15,290 --> 00:18:17,530
the Imperial Court Exam
is the main course.

344
00:18:16,420 --> 00:18:17,010
[Xu Yourong]

345
00:18:17,050 --> 00:18:17,130
[Guan Feibai]

346
00:18:17,560 --> 00:18:19,760
How far can you go?

